'''Blerim Hasalla''' (born 13 September 1976) is an [[Albania]]n [[football defender]]<ref>[http://www.transfermarkt.de/de/spieler/99099/hasalla-blerim/profil.html Transfermarkt Profile]</ref> who currently plays for [[KS Tomori Berat]] in the [[Albanian First Division]].<ref>[http://footballdatabase.eu/football.joueurs.blerim.hasalla.53311.en.html Footballdatabase Profile]</ref>
== Honours == === Besa === * [[Albanian Cup]] (1): 2009-10
